    {
      "chinese": "日本人來了之後，在靠近北大武主峰旁的「tjukazangiljan」設了神社，為了表彰到南洋島嶼作戰的族人們。故此讓大武山周邊的部落族人，攜帶沙子、石塊前往大武山建立神社，也就是現在許多人渴望登頂觀賞的景點。",
      "ab": "kamangetjez a zipung, masengeseng tiamadju tua kakisukuban, a sinsiya a pimaza i tjukazangiljan, tua kakisukuban katu kakipaqenetjan, taicu a navaik a pasanavalj, i ta vuguvug, a nakiqeciyan ta tjai sangasangas. nasemekaulj ta mareka qinaljan i palingulj i tjagaraus tu semakuc tua vudas tua qaciljay, tu silingedjelj tua kakisukuban. sa tucu  avan anga nu sivaivaik a ljemizav nu namaqusav tu natalidu a timaimanga.",
      "order": "3",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2021/03/07/58c41cd70e5338ee98e64cff737f3789.wav",
      "word": [
        {
          "ab": "kamangetjez",
          "ch": "來到",
          "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2021/05/23/7a91b368cb07182b515187fe411969e6.wav"
        },
        {
